---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Software Development Services</h1>
	<p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-4">We specialize in building custom software that solves real business problems.</p>
	<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
		<div class="p-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Custom Applications</h2>
			<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Unique software solutions built from the ground up to support your specific business processes and growth objectives.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="p-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Internal Tooling</h2>
			<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Boost your team's productivity with workflow management systems, automation scripts, and administrative tools designed specifically for your operations.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="p-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">API Integrations</h2>
			<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Connect your existing software ecosystem to ensure data flows seamlessly between your critical business platforms.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="p-8 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Technical Strategy</h2>
			<p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Practical guidance on choosing the right tech stack and architecture to ensure your software is scalable and maintainable.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
